Revision history for Dist-Zilla-PERLANCAR-CheckDepDists

0.05    2016-02-14 (PERLANCAR)

	- Find Bencher-Scenario dists that require our dist and alert a
	  reminder to rebuild them.


0.04    2015-07-28 (PERLANCAR)

	- Search for .tag-requires-dist-<DISTNAME> tag files.


0.03    2015-07-09 (PERLANCAR)

	- Also search packed dists in ::FatPacked and ::DataPacked.


0.02    2015-07-06 (PERLANCAR)

	- Now support packed (depak) dists instead of fattened dists.


0.01     2015-05-16 (PERLANCAR)

         - First release.
